{"database_schema": ""Description for table: Deposit"
type Deposit implements Event @entity(immutable: true) @transaction {
  "Unique identifier for the deposit event"
  id: Bytes!
  "Hash of the transaction associated with the deposit"
  hash: Bytes!
  "Index of the log entry in the block"
  logIndex: Int!
  "Protocol associated with the deposit"
  protocol: Protocol!
  "Address receiving the deposit"
  to: Bytes!
  "Address from which the deposit is sent"
  from: Bytes!
  "Address of the depositor"
  depositor: Bytes!
  "Pool involved in the deposit"
  pool: Pool!
  "Token being deposited"
  token: Token!
  "Number of shares received in exchange for the deposit"
  shares: BigInt!
  "Amount of tokens deposited"
  amount: BigInt!
  "Value of the deposit in USD"
  amountUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Block number when the deposit was recorded"
  blockNumber: BigInt!
  "Timestamp of when the deposit occurred"
  timestamp: BigInt!
}"}
